snippet.title: Europa Universalis IV: Emperor - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Rule as the Emperor to rewrite history and remake the world. Europa Universalis IV: Emperor is the latest expansion to Paradox Development Studio’s flagship series, Europa Universalis IV. This add-on  returns its focus to Europe. Available now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1259360/Expansion__Europa_Universalis_IV_Emperor/
